BARD COMMUNICATION

Bards are social by design. These commands help you stay connected with other
Bards and with the guild.

  bard <message>
    Speak on the Bard guild channel.

  : <message>
    Send a Bard emote.

  bemotes
    List available Bard emotes.

  bardhist
    Review recent Bard channel history.

  bards
    List Bards currently online.

  bgm <message>
    Guild master channel. Requires guild level 11.

  bgmhist
    Review recent Bard guild master channel history.

Bards also learn more racial languages than most guilds. Communication is part
of the guild's identity, not just a convenience.
